American Arts Incubator-South Africa: This creative exchange is a cross-institutional programme that uses of community-driven digital and new media art projects to strengthen local economies, encourage innovation and deals with social and environmental issues. Comic book creator and documentary filmmaker Ram Devineni is leading the programme Details: The programme runs until June 5 at the KwaZulu-Natal Society of Arts gallery, 166 Bulwer Road, Durban.
